ABI baseline dump placeholder.

The ABI dump for this directory is generated at release time using:

    abi-dumper libomega.so -o abi/omega-<VERSION>.dump -lver <VERSION>

The baseline is committed to abi/ after tagging v0.1.0 and serves as the
reference for the abidiff CI job on subsequent PRs.

The abidiff CI job is a no-op until this placeholder is replaced by a real
.dump file. See docs/design/12-library-foundation.md §2.3.
